none.description:
{Base Darkness}

A thick shroud of darkness envelops the area surrounding the hero (3 radius), obscuring it from the sight of foes.

The spell inflicts a -2 penalty to Knowledge, decreases visibility radius by -3, and reduces the hero’s movement by -1000 points. The effects persist until the next week.

